HEADWORD: Evolvent
<hw>E*volv"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>evolvens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, unrolling, p. pr. of
<ets>evolvere</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Geom.)</fld> <def>The involute of a
